Any of action buttons exclude <button onclick="Android.prefButtonCallback()"> {{{btnSettings}}} </button> and <button onclick="BLOCK_Android.editButtonCallback(PFN)"> {{{btnEdit}}} </button> can be disabled or enabled.
This option effective only at html page creation time. If you want to add remove buttons on already created page you need to set option an regenerate (delete and the visit) html page.

